001
002package com.commercetools.api.models.custom_object;
003
004import java.time.ZonedDateTime;
005import java.util.function.Function;
006
007import javax.validation.Valid;
008import javax.validation.constraints.NotNull;
009
010import com.commercetools.api.models.Referencable;
011import com.commercetools.api.models.common.*;
012import com.fasterxml.jackson.annotation.JsonProperty;
013import com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.annotation.JsonDeserialize;
014
015/**
016 * entity to implement a type safe generic custom object
017 * @param <TValue> The type of the value of this custom object.
018 */
019@JsonDeserialize(as = GenericCustomObjectImpl.class)
020public interface GenericCustomObject<TValue>
021        extends BaseResource, com.commercetools.api.models.DomainResource<GenericCustomObject<TValue>>,
022        Referencable<GenericCustomObject<TValue>> {
023
024    @NotNull
025    @JsonProperty("id")
026    public String getId();
027
028    @NotNull
029    @JsonProperty("version")
030    public Long getVersion();
031
032    @NotNull
033    @JsonProperty("createdAt")
034    public ZonedDateTime getCreatedAt();
035
036    @NotNull
037    @JsonProperty("lastModifiedAt")
038    public ZonedDateTime getLastModifiedAt();
039
040    /**
041    *  <p>Present on resources created after 2019-02-01 except for <a href="/client-logging#events-tracked">events not tracked</a>.</p>
042    * @return LastModifiedBy
043    */
044    @Valid
045    @JsonProperty("lastModifiedBy")
046    public LastModifiedBy getLastModifiedBy();
047
048    /**
049    *  <p>Present on resources created after 2019-02-01 except for <a href="/client-logging#events-tracked">events not tracked</a>.</p>
050     * @return CreatedBy
051    */
052    @Valid
053    @JsonProperty("createdBy")
054    public CreatedBy getCreatedBy();
055
056    /**
057     *  <p>A namespace to group custom objects.</p>
058     * @return container name
059     */
060    @NotNull
061    @JsonProperty("container")
062    public String getContainer();
063
064    @NotNull
065    @JsonProperty("key")
066    public String getKey();
067
068    @NotNull
069    @JsonProperty("value")
070    public TValue getValue();
071
072    public void setId(final String id);
073
074    public void setVersion(final Long version);
075
076    public void setCreatedAt(final ZonedDateTime createdAt);
077
078    public void setLastModifiedAt(final ZonedDateTime lastModifiedAt);
079
080    public void setLastModifiedBy(final LastModifiedBy lastModifiedBy);
081
082    public void setCreatedBy(final CreatedBy createdBy);
083
084    public void setContainer(final String container);
085
086    public void setKey(final String key);
087
088    public void setValue(final TValue value);
089
090    public static <T> GenericCustomObject<T> of() {
091        return new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>();
092    }
093
094    public static <T> GenericCustomObject<T> of(final GenericCustomObject<T> template) {
095        GenericCustomObjectImpl<T> instance = new GenericCustomObjectImpl<>();
096        instance.setId(template.getId());
097        instance.setVersion(template.getVersion());
098        instance.setCreatedAt(template.getCreatedAt());
099        instance.setLastModifiedAt(template.getLastModifiedAt());
100        instance.setLastModifiedBy(template.getLastModifiedBy());
101        instance.setCreatedBy(template.getCreatedBy());
102        instance.setContainer(template.getContainer());
103        instance.setKey(template.getKey());
104        instance.setValue(template.getValue());
105        return instance;
106    }
107
108    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> builder(T value) {
109        return GenericCustomObjectBuilder.of(value);
110    }
111
112    public static <T> GenericCustomObjectBuilder<T> builder(final GenericCustomObject<T> template) {
113        return GenericCustomObjectBuilder.of(template);
114    }
115
116    default <T> T withCustomObject(Function<GenericCustomObject<TValue>, T> helper) {
117        return helper.apply(this);
118    }
119
120    @Override
121    default Reference toReference() {
122        return CustomObjectReference.builder().id(getId()).build();
123    }
124}
